{"tw": {"4216930": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Wicked Ways", "steam_appid": 4216930, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/8e8a978aed840833555d42fa08a798e7.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><strong>Wicked Ways</strong> 是一款成人視覺小說，讓你扮演一家廣告代理公司中冉冉升起的創意總監。在一個由形象和影響力塑造的世界裡，在野心與慾望之間周旋，與拿下下一個大提案同樣重要。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/3804b9d221ef165732029d715a7e9145.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在平衡事業需求與日益複雜的私人生活時，你將發現自己陷入了一個充滿浪漫和微妙道德抉擇的網絡中。遊戲將生活化的敘事與交織的浪漫動態相結合，讓你做出的決定往往模糊了忠誠與激情之間的界限。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/1e57b234d26763e05c9ef22eb49fa439.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生活即是你的靈感</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/895c4982bae12c678f20b049aff9f68e.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Wicked Ways》中，創意源於你周圍的世界。一個轉瞬即逝的眼神、一次坦誠的對話或一個微妙的手勢，都能為你下一個廣告企劃點燃靈感的火花。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/d68b15da32f3b1c065005410dfdd5fcb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的人際關係和經歷可以激發職業上的成功，將情感轉化為能夠打動客戶並在同事心中留下印記的作品。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/7e93a87249e6f96a15ce3f347ffabf06.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>複雜多面的角色陣容</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/514b94e0a3eeb490040d8b14b3d4a0d4.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路上，你會遇到各種各樣迷人的女性，她們每個人都有獨特的個性、隱藏的動機和層層疊疊的過往。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/9f90d1a10dedefa1358e28801b29908b.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從喜歡調情的同事到過去熟悉的面孔，每一次互動都提供了探索羈絆、親密關係和影響力的機會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定義你的道路</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/64050e797bb186ef508c1ecf4c1e5636.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著事業的發展，野心與浪漫自然而然地交織在一起。辦公室裡的邂逅、深夜的傾訴以及意想不到的會面，創造出種種時刻，考驗著你的忠誠、慾望以及在微妙的情感局勢中游刃有餘的能力。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/2b00b4857a8fe0a39dddb2e6a60ad91c.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的選擇至關重要</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/07d72abd4ed59aa0f7efce1b141feebb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一個決定不僅塑造著你的愛情生活，也影響著你的職業地位和你周圍的社交圈。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/b816b1710ff795c0eca7a9ed18598f20.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >準備好踏上一段誘惑無處不在的旅程吧。你的決定將塑造接下來的劇情，並定義在這個充滿錯綜複雜關係和隱藏慾望的世界裡，你會成為什麼樣的人。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/bdba786582090998ca9749672ff53d72.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/c999105dccab06790dcdf918ae5e7e5f.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/a4cbbb2f7155fdcc8ef1ac135e20610d.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/080a6e0039909ba882ce556b2c088936.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/36ae95dd3cf109d878b1de083efed929.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/8e8a978aed840833555d42fa08a798e7.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><strong>Wicked Ways</strong> 是一款成人視覺小說，讓你扮演一家廣告代理公司中冉冉升起的創意總監。在一個由形象和影響力塑造的世界裡，在野心與慾望之間周旋，與拿下下一個大提案同樣重要。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/3804b9d221ef165732029d715a7e9145.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在平衡事業需求與日益複雜的私人生活時，你將發現自己陷入了一個充滿浪漫和微妙道德抉擇的網絡中。遊戲將生活化的敘事與交織的浪漫動態相結合，讓你做出的決定往往模糊了忠誠與激情之間的界限。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/1e57b234d26763e05c9ef22eb49fa439.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生活即是你的靈感</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/895c4982bae12c678f20b049aff9f68e.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Wicked Ways》中，創意源於你周圍的世界。一個轉瞬即逝的眼神、一次坦誠的對話或一個微妙的手勢，都能為你下一個廣告企劃點燃靈感的火花。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/d68b15da32f3b1c065005410dfdd5fcb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的人際關係和經歷可以激發職業上的成功，將情感轉化為能夠打動客戶並在同事心中留下印記的作品。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/7e93a87249e6f96a15ce3f347ffabf06.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>複雜多面的角色陣容</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/514b94e0a3eeb490040d8b14b3d4a0d4.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路上，你會遇到各種各樣迷人的女性，她們每個人都有獨特的個性、隱藏的動機和層層疊疊的過往。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/9f90d1a10dedefa1358e28801b29908b.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從喜歡調情的同事到過去熟悉的面孔，每一次互動都提供了探索羈絆、親密關係和影響力的機會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定義你的道路</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/64050e797bb186ef508c1ecf4c1e5636.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著事業的發展，野心與浪漫自然而然地交織在一起。辦公室裡的邂逅、深夜的傾訴以及意想不到的會面，創造出種種時刻，考驗著你的忠誠、慾望以及在微妙的情感局勢中游刃有餘的能力。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/2b00b4857a8fe0a39dddb2e6a60ad91c.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的選擇至關重要</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/07d72abd4ed59aa0f7efce1b141feebb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一個決定不僅塑造著你的愛情生活，也影響著你的職業地位和你周圍的社交圈。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/b816b1710ff795c0eca7a9ed18598f20.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >準備好踏上一段誘惑無處不在的旅程吧。你的決定將塑造接下來的劇情，並定義在這個充滿錯綜複雜關係和隱藏慾望的世界裡，你會成為什麼樣的人。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/bdba786582090998ca9749672ff53d72.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/c999105dccab06790dcdf918ae5e7e5f.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/a4cbbb2f7155fdcc8ef1ac135e20610d.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/080a6e0039909ba882ce556b2c088936.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/36ae95dd3cf109d878b1de083efed929.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>", "short_description": "《Wicked Ways》是一款成人視覺小說，帶你遊走於錯綜複雜的關係網。在野心與慾望之間尋求平衡，做出的選擇將模糊忠誠與親密的界限。在這個每次互動都舉足輕重的世界裡，探索隱藏的深意。", "supported_languages": "英文, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 捷克文, 日文, 韓文, 波蘭文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 俄文, 簡體中文, 泰文, 繁體中文, 土耳其文, 烏克蘭文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/c81ca6042ec91ecbd2f3b7649627c4d04022b391/header.jpg?t=1775328450", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/4d73d71e9eab7b56a36990e9e2ebeb3050a639ec/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1775328450", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/4d73d71e9eab7b56a36990e9e2ebeb3050a639ec/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1775328450", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 (64-bit) or higher<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 Ghz Intel-compatible or equivalent AMD CPU<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 3.0 or DirectX 11 compatible<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> 10.10+ (Yosemite)<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 Ghz 64-bit Intel-compatible or Apple M1 (ARM) series<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 3.0 compatible<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 20.04+ (64-bit) or equivalent distribution<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 Ghz Intel-compatible or equivalent AMD CPU<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 3.0 compatible<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}, "us": {"4216930": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Wicked Ways", "steam_appid": 4216930, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/8e8a978aed840833555d42fa08a798e7.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><strong>Wicked Ways</strong> is an adult visual novel that puts you in the shoes of a rising Creative Director at an advertising agency. In a world shaped by image and influence, navigating ambition and desire is just as important as making the next big pitch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/3804b9d221ef165732029d715a7e9145.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>As you balance the demands of your career with an increasingly intricate personal life, you will find yourself drawn into a network of romance and subtle moral choices. Blending slice-of-life storytelling with intertwined romantic dynamics, the game lets you make decisions that often blur the lines between loyalty and passion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/1e57b234d26763e05c9ef22eb49fa439.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>LIFE IS YOUR INSPIRATION</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/895c4982bae12c678f20b049aff9f68e.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Creativity in Wicked Ways comes from the world around you. A fleeting glance, a candid conversation, or a subtle gesture can spark ideas for your next campaign.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/d68b15da32f3b1c065005410dfdd5fcb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Your personal relationships and experiences can inspire professional success, transforming emotion into work that captivates clients and leaves a mark on colleagues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/7e93a87249e6f96a15ce3f347ffabf06.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A CAST OF COMPLEX CHARACTERS</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/514b94e0a3eeb490040d8b14b3d4a0d4.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Along the way, you will meet a variety of compelling women, each with distinct personalities, hidden motivations, and layered histories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/9f90d1a10dedefa1358e28801b29908b.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>From flirtatious coworkers to familiar faces from the past, every interaction offers opportunities to explore connection, intimacy, and influence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>DEFINE YOUR PATH</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/64050e797bb186ef508c1ecf4c1e5636.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>As your career progresses, ambition and romance naturally intertwine. Office encounters, late-night confessions, and unexpected meetings create moments that test loyalty, desire, and your ability to navigate a delicate emotional landscape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/2b00b4857a8fe0a39dddb2e6a60ad91c.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>YOUR CHOICES MATTER</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/07d72abd4ed59aa0f7efce1b141feebb.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Every decision shapes not only your love life but also your professional standing and the social circles around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/b816b1710ff795c0eca7a9ed18598f20.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Get ready for a journey where temptation is never far away. Your decisions will shape the unfolding drama and define who you become in a world of convoluted relationships and hidden desires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4216930/extras/bdba786582090998ca9749672ff53d72.avif?t=1775328450\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/421693